pageContext.claim: “Today, you saw it. I hit my highest poll numbers since I got elected because the American people, and frankly, people all over the world know it's a hoax. They understand it. They know it's a hoax.”
pageContext.analysis: Nope, Trump was still in the low 40 percent approval range. He had been higher months before and shortly after taking office, according to FiveThirtyEight.
